{"tid":190265,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為黑人爭取公義　 美國穆斯林學生獲史丹福大學取錄","createTime":"2017-04-07T04:14:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-09T05:13:10.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5ffc90c0d0f90ecb11a18876ac7e6d41b9b185b0","tid":190265,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T04:14:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1765000/1765094/BlackLivesMatter_thumb_20170406_J_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1765000%2F1765094%2FBlackLivesMatter_thumb_20170406_J_1024.jpg&h=fd6940ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n學生想考入名牌大學往往要「爭崩頭」，何況是美國的史丹福大學？面對史丹福大學20人爭1學位的競爭，除了靠優異的成績外，亦有考生以申請時的自我介紹(Personal Statement)突圍而出。<br />\n<br />\n美國新澤西州的18歲孟加拉裔穆斯林高中學生Ziad Ahmed，於自我介紹上寫上100次的#BlackLivesMatter(#黑人命也是命)，獲史丹福大學取錄。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》報導，Ziad Ahmed於他的Twitter上分享了他的自我介紹，題目是「對你而言，甚麼是重要的？」(What matters to you, and why?)。Ziad Ahmed只填上黑人維權口號#BlackLivesMatter(#黑人命也是命)100次。答案一出，竟獲史丹福大學取錄，是Ziad Ahmed始料未及的結果：<br />\n<br />\n我本來覺得自己不會被史丹福大學取錄，對於我如此不客氣的言行，史丹福大學仍能看成是一個個人優點而非負累，的確讓人喜出望外。<br />\nZiad Ahmed表示，黑人長年累月被剝削、被打壓，他們有責任為黑人發聲，透過語言、想法及行動賦予黑人權力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然Ziad Ahmed一發文旋即受到8000人轉載，不過留言並非一面倒支持他。有網民留言批評他只是在做門面功夫(virtue signalling)，扮作激進，但獲史丹福大學取錄的原因，並非單憑100次#BlackLivesMatter，而是Ziad Ahmed是一個擁有優異成績及成就的年輕人。<br />\n<br />\n早於申請史丹福大學之前，Ziad Ahmed曾為希拉莉助選總統，亦曾獲歐巴馬邀請參觀白宮，開始參與政治活動。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1765000/1765094/hilaryclinton_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1765000%2F1765094%2Fhilaryclinton_1024.jpg&h=620dacfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">Ziad Ahmed曾於去年為希拉莉助選。(相片來源：Ziad Ahmed Instagram)</span><br />\n<br />\n另外，他又創立了性別平權組織redefy，與一眾年輕人成立了JUV Consulting並成為CVO，曾被MTV選為改變世界的9大青少年(MTV's Top 9 Teens Changing the World)，以及Business Insider評選為15位天才少年的其中1人。除了以上名銜外，Ziad Ahmed亦曾在演講平台TED發表演說。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n18歲便擁有如此亮眼的成就，難怪寫上100次#BlackLivesMatter就得到史丹福大學賞識，考入名校。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1765094/%E7%82%BA%E9%BB%91%E4%BA%BA%E7%88%AD%E5%8F%96%E5%85%AC%E7%BE%A9%E3%80%80%E4%BB%96%E5%AF%AB%E7%B5%A6%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%B9%E7%A6%8F%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%9A%84%E5%85%A5%E5%AD%B8%E4%BF%A1?mtc=10001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1765094%2F%25E7%2582%25BA%25E9%25BB%2591%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2588%25AD%25E5%258F%2596%25E5%2585%25AC%25E7%25BE%25A9%25E3%2580%2580%25E4%25BB%2596%25E5%25AF%25AB%25E7%25B5%25A6%25E5%258F%25B2%25E4%25B8%25B9%25E7%25A6%258F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E4%25BF%25A1%3Fmtc%3D10001&d=2%2B%2BG2pXT7lWIneVuf1o%2BJBxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=d0336ce3\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1765094/%E7%82%BA%E9%BB%91%E4%BA%BA%E7%88%AD%E5%8F%96%E5%85%AC%E7%BE%A9%E3%80%80%E4%BB%96%E5%AF%AB%E7%B5%A6%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%B9%E7%A6%8F%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%9A%84%E5%85%A5%E5%AD%B8%E4%BF%A1?mtc=10001</a>"},{"pid":"21c065786ec136b614bcc33e608870534fab5763","tid":190265,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T04:18:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c438793a380ef609fe1bf87a3de2e91b9835da46","tid":190265,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T04:34:50.000Z","msg":"曾為希拉莉助選總統，亦曾獲歐巴馬邀請參觀白宮<br />\n<br />\n係咪代表寫乜都得？"},{"pid":"064efd347381460843863b56e921bac856be9b48","tid":190265,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T04:39:41.000Z","msg":"All lives matter"},{"pid":"5fbe5838e337aa70524d349c5f1d51773d32b1d8","tid":190265,"uid":15758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T04:41:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>曾為希拉莉助選總統，亦曾獲歐巴馬邀請參觀白宮<br />\n<br />\n係咪代表寫乜都得？</blockquote><br />\n曾在廁所開大，亦曾在大型商場購